PODPING_DB_CONNECTION = "mongodb://adam-v4vapp:27017/"

time_limit = timedelta(days =1)
earliest_data = datetime.utcnow() - time_limit
MONGO_CLIENT = AsyncIOMotorClient(PODPING_DB_CONNECTION)
MONGO_DB = MONGO_CLIENT["podping_data"]

cursor = MONGO_DB["rc_history"].find({"timestamp": {"$gte" : earliest_data}}, {"_id": 0})
data = []
async for doc in cursor:
    data.append(doc)

df = pd.DataFrame(data)
utc = datetime.utcnow()

df["age"] = utc - df["timestamp"] 
df = df.set_index("timestamp")

time_limit = timedelta(days =1)
earliest_data = datetime.utcnow() - time_limit

cursor = MONGO_DB["podping_history"].find({"timestamp": {"$gte" : earliest_data}} ,{"_id": 0})
data = []
async for doc in cursor:
    data.append(doc)

pp = pd.DataFrame(data)
pp["age"] = datetime.utcnow() - pp["timestamp"]
pp["age_hours"] = pp["age"].dt.total_seconds()/3600


def draw_graph_podpings(hive_accname):
    if not pp[pp.hive_accname == hive_accname].empty:
        ppf = pp[pp.hive_accname == hive_accname].copy()
        ppf = ppf.set_index(ppf.age_hours)
        fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,1, figsize =(10, 6), layout='constrained')   
        ppf['Cumulative Num Pings'] = ppf.age_hours.rank(method = 'average', pct = False)    
        ax.plot(ppf.age_hours, ppf['Cumulative Num Pings'])
        ax.set_ylabel("Cumulative Num Podpings")
        ax.set_xlabel("Age in Hours")
        ax.set_title(f"Podpings by {hive_accname}") 
        ax.invert_xaxis()
        ax.invert_yaxis()
        plt.show()
    # ppf.plot(x = 'age_hours', y = 'Cumulative Num Pings', grid = True)

def draw_graph_rc(hive_accname):
    df1 = df[df.hive_accname ==hive_accname]

    fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,1, figsize =(10, 6), layout='constrained')           
    ax.plot(df1.rc.sort_index(), label="Resource Credits RCs")
    ax.set_title(f"Resource Credits of {hive_accname}")
    ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(
        mdates.ConciseDateFormatter(ax.xaxis.get_major_locator()))
    ax.set_ylabel("RC Percentage")
    ax2 = ax.twinx()
    ax2.set_ylabel("Hive Power")
    ax2.plot(df1.hive_power, color="red", label="Hive Power HP", linewidth=3)

    ax2.set_ymargin(2)
    ax2.set_ylim(bottom = 0, top= df1.hive_power.max() * 1.02)

    fig.legend(loc="lower left", bbox_to_anchor=(0.2,0.1))
    plt.show()
